						<h2 class="pagetitle">Function Reference/the permalink</h2>
									<!-- start content -->
				<p class="LanguageLinks" style="border:1px solid #CCCCCC; line-height:1.5; text-align:left; color:#333333; font-size:90%; padding:10px;"><span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/Multilingual_Codex" title="Multilingual Codex" class="mw-redirect">Languages</a>:</span> 
<a href="/Template_Tags/the_permalink" title="Template Tags/the permalink" class="mw-redirect">English</a> • 
<a href="http://wpdocs.sourceforge.jp/%E3%83%86%E3%83%B3%E3%83%97%E3%83%AC%E3%83%BC%E3%83%88%E3%82%BF%E3%82%B0/the_permalink" class="external text" title="http://wpdocs.sourceforge.jp/%E3%83%86%E3%83%B3%E3%83%97%E3%83%AC%E3%83%BC%E3%83%88%E3%82%BF%E3%82%B0/the_permalink">日本語</a> • 
 <small>(<a href="/Multilingual_Codex#Language_Cross_Reference" title="Multilingual Codex" class="mw-redirect">Add your language</a>)</small>
</p>
