</li><li> File renamed to <code><a href="http://core.trac.wordpress.org/browser/tags/2.1/wp-includes/link-template.php#L4" class="external text" title="http://core.trac.wordpress.org/browser/tags/2.1/wp-includes/link-template.php#L4">wp-includes/link-template.php</a></code> in <a href="/Version_2.1" title="Version 2.1">2.1</a>
</li></ul>
<a name="Source_File" id="Source_File"></a><h2> <span class="mw-headline"> Source File </span></h2>
<p><tt>the_permalink()</tt> is located in <code><a href="http://core.trac.wordpress.org/browser/tags/3.5.1/wp-includes/link-template.php#L0" class="external text" title="http://core.trac.wordpress.org/browser/tags/3.5.1/wp-includes/link-template.php#L0">wp-includes/link-template.php</a></code>.
</p>
